③-④得 | lP_l = tP_l' - P_{l-1}' | ⑤
由⑤，令t=0，则 lP_l(0) = -P_{l-1}'(0)
P_{l-1}'(0) = -lP_l(0).
P_l'(0) = -(l+1)P_{l+1}(0).
而 P_l(0) = \frac{1}{\pi} \int_0^\pi \sin^l \phi d\phi = \begin{cases} 1, l=0 \\ 0, l为奇数 \\ \frac{2}{\pi} \cdot \frac{(l-1)!!}{l!!} \cdot \frac{\pi}{2} = (-1)^{l/2} \frac{(l-1)!!}{l!!}, l为偶数 \end{cases}
故 P_l'(0) = \begin{cases} 0, l+1为奇数 \\ -(l+1) \cdot (-1)^{(l+1)/2} \frac{l!!}{(l+1)!!}, l+1为偶数 \end{cases}
(-1)^{\frac{l+1}{2}} \frac{l!!}{(l-1)!!}

